snippet.title: Doomed PETSCII Pacman - a C64 PETSCII game
snippet.description:
Descend into a realm where classic Pacman meets perilous twists! Dare to play this PETSCII game with its wickedly new rules on the Commodore 64?

Play online here: https://c64online.com/c64-games/doomed-petscii-pacman/
